<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٦٥٩]</span> أَبُو مَعْنٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سمِعَ ابنَ عُمرَ، وجَابِرَ بنَ زَيدٍ، وابنَ الزُّبَيرِ، وأبا العَالِيةِ، وأَنَسًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رَوى عنهُ مُعْتمرُ بنُ سُلَيمانَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٦٦٠]</span> أَبُو مَعْنٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>عنِ ابنِ سِيرينَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>رَوى عنهُ مَسْعَدةُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٦٦١]</span> أَبُو مَعْنٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
